---
// AboutMe.astro
---

<div class="about-content">
  <div class="intro">
    <h3>Hello, I'm KTTLSAA</h3>
    <p>
      I'm a researcher and developer exploring the intersection of epistemology, anthropology, and software development. My work focuses on how we build, share, and interact with knowledge in digital spaces.
    </p>
    <p>
      I believe that personal knowledge systems can transform how we think and learn.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="more-link">
    <a href="/about-extended" class="button">More About Me</a>
  </div> 
  
  <div class="newsletter">
    <h3>Stay Updated</h3>
    <p>Subscribe to receive updates when I add new notes, essays, or projects to this digital garden.</p>
    <form class="subscribe-form">
      <input type="email" placeholder="Your email address" required />
      <button type="submit">SUBSCRIBE</button>
    </form>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }

  .intro p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-s);
  }

  .core-values ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .core-values li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    padding-left: var(--space-s);
    position: relative;
  }

  .core-values li::before {
    content: "â€¢";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .newsletter {
    margin-top: var(--space-m);
    padding: var(--space-m);
    background-color: var(--bg-color-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius-m);
  }

  .subscribe-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    margin-top: var(--space-s);
  }

  .subscribe-form input {
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-s);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius-s);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .subscribe-form button {
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-s);
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: var(--radius-s);
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .subscribe-form button:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }

  .more-link {
    margin-top: var(--space-m);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .more-link .button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-s);
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-s);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .more-link .button:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
</style>

